<![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008">
<p>If <span fontStyle="italic">c</span> and <span fontStyle="italic">d</span> are odd positive integers, which of the following could be odd?</p>
<p></p>
<p>Indicate <span textDecoration="underline">all</span> such expressions.</p>
</TextFlow>]]>
</barrons:question>

